	  Fix the homepage of LAME. The old www.mp3dev.org is pointing to
	  the
	  sourceforge page.

2020-08-19 13:13  aleidinger

	* libmp3lame/i386/nasm.h:
	  Fix nasm include file (UTF-8 BOM which nasm does't know about).
	  
