2011-03-02 16:54  rbrito

	* debian/control:
	  Remove unused Conflicts: and Replaces: fields.
	  
	  They were never part of any stable release and 3rd party sites
	  were,
	  perhaps, faster than us in providing changed packages (when the
	  packaging
	  was not up-to-date).

