2005-11-28 10:09  vitaly-ivanov

	* dshow/Encoder.h, dshow/Mpegac.cpp, dshow/Mpegac.h,
	  dshow/PropPage.cpp, dshow/PropPage.h, dshow/PropPage_adv.cpp,
