	* frontend/parse.c, libmp3lame/lame.c,
	  libmp3lame/lame_global_flags.h, libmp3lame/set_get.c:
	  added internal developer switch to select between ISO and x^3/4
	  quantization
	  
	  --quantization-type n n=0: no change, n=1: ISO, n=2: x^3/4

