2001-03-26 00:38  markt

	* frontend/brhist.c:
	  bug in brhist_disp_total()
	  
	  for --freeformat bmode, br_frames = 0 (why?)
	  so sum / br_frames would segfault.
	  
	  if br_frames == 0 , routine now just returns without printing
	  anything.

