	  vbrquantize.c:
	  more massive internal changes in the goal of making
	  lame thread safe.
	  
	  gfp-> user controlled varialbes
	  gfc-> all other internal parameters. eventually all global
	  variables
	  which very from encode to encode need to go in here.

