	  Added mpega.library support for decoding mpeg audio, enable with
	  AMIGA_MPEGA. (AmigaOS)

2000-01-10 00:45  markt

	* loopold.c, quantize.c:
	  fixed bug in loopold: scalesave loop was using SBMAX instead of
	  SBPSY,
	  and exceeding bounds.

