	* Dll/BladeMP3EncDLL.c, Dll/BladeMP3EncDLL.def,
	  Dll/BladeMP3EncDLL.h, Dll/MP3EncDll.dsp, Dll/MP3EncDll.dsw:
	  Update of Blade DLL interface in order to support new lame
	  features

